#### Enums

##### `EntryKind`

Persistence semantics applied to a stored entry

Passed as `i32` discriminant.

| Variant | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `Volatile` | `0` |
| `Persistent` | `1` |
| `Encrypted` | `2` |

